"You can then modify any of the colors by clicking the color button, which "
"will open color select palette. This will provide unlimited options in color "
"selection. You can select a defined basic color, pick a color by clicking "
"anywhere on the displayed color palette, input an &HTML; defined color, or "
"specify values for Hue, Saturation, Value, Red, Green, and Blue."
msgstr ""

